org.apache.flex.compiler.codegen.mxml

Interface IMXMLEmitter

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEmitter
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IMXMLFlexJSEmitter
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MXMLEmitter, MXMLFlexJSEmitter, MXMLJSCJSEmitter, MXMLVF2JSEmitter

    public interface IMXMLEmitter
extends IEmitter
    The IMXMLEmitter interface allows abstraction between the IASNodeStrategy and the current output buffer Writer.
    Author:
    Michael Schmalle, Erik de Bruin
